data.name: Exit_Criteria_Update_Flag_Banner_Inactive_Wave_1
data.queryText:
SELECT a.PersonContactId, c.Contact_Entry_DE, 'Home banner changed and exited' as [Exit From], 
GETDATE() as [Exit Time]
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/2c537478-19d0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/2c537478-19d0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/name}}] a
JOIN {{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/8277c6ad-4e3a-ed11-ba3c-d4f5ef3de461/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/8277c6ad-4e3a-ed11-ba3c-d4f5ef3de461/data/name}}] b
ON SUBSTRING(a.AirmilesNumber,1,10) = b.CUSTOMER_CARD_ID
JOIN {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/ca9e6427-1ad0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/ca9e6427-1ad0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/name}}] c
ON a.PersonContactId = c.PersonContactId
WHERE b.HomeS_Banner != 'SOBEYS'
AND ([Exit Time] ='' OR [Exit Time] IS NULL )

data.name: Banner_Inactive_Tracking_Wave_1
data.queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT PersonContactId, POSID,BannerAccountUser_Id, Account_FirstName, Account_LastName, Account_PersonEmail, 
Email_optin, Email_optout, Account_global_opt_out__c, 
Contact_Entry_DE, Region, AirmilesNumber
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/2c537478-19d0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/2c537478-19d0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/name}}] entry
WHERE NOT EXISTS
	(SELECT DISTINCT PersonContactId
	FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/ca9e6427-1ad0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/ca9e6427-1ad0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/name}}] track
	WHERE
		entry.PersonContactId = track.PersonContactId
		AND entry.Contact_Entry_DE = track.Contact_Entry_DE)

data.name: Update_Region_Banner_Inactive_Wave_1
data.queryText:
SELECT bia.BannerAccountUser_Id, cr.sobeys_mapping as Region, postal_first_letter as Postal_Code, PersonContactId
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/4ffc0da0-74a9-eb11-a2fe-48df370f018d/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/4ffc0da0-74a9-eb11-a2fe-48df370f018d/data/name}}] cr
JOIN {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/2c537478-19d0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/2c537478-19d0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/name}}] bia
ON Postal_Code = UPPER(postal_first_letter)

data.name: Exit_Criteria_Global_Suppression_Banner_Inactive_Wave_1
data.queryText:
SELECT a.PersonContactId, a.Contact_Entry_DE, 'Global Suppression is true exited' as [Exit From], 
GETDATE() as [Exit Time]
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/ca9e6427-1ad0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/ca9e6427-1ad0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/name}}] a
JOIN {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/f2acf0bb-d606-eb11-a2f2-48df370f0128/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/f2acf0bb-d606-eb11-a2f2-48df370f0128/data/name}}] b
ON a.PersonContactId = b.PersonContactId
WHERE b.Global_Suppression_Flag = 'True' 
AND ([Exit Time] ='' OR [Exit Time] IS NULL)

data.name: Banner_Inactive_Wave_1
data.queryText:
SELECT
	DISTINCT cma.PersonContactId,
	cma.BannerAccountUser_Id,
	cma.BannerAccount_Id,
	cma.Account_FirstName,
	cma.Account_LastName,
	cma.Account_PersonEmail,
	cma.Email_optin,
	cma.Email_optout,
	cma.Account_global_opt_out__c,
	GETDATE() AS Contact_Entry,
	cma.Account_uid__c AS UID,
	cma.Account_SFSC_airmiles__c AS AirmilesNumber,
	CASE
		WHEN Account_postalCode__c IS NOT NULL THEN UPPER(SUBSTRING(Account_postalCode__c, 1, 1))
		WHEN Account_postalCode__c IS NULL THEN 'Default'
		WHEN Account_postalCode__c = '' THEN 'Default'
	END AS postal_code,
	[{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/1fe7caea-ae87-eb11-a2fb-48df370ead2d/data/name}}].SEGMENT,
        CASE
                WHEN [{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/1fe7caea-ae87-eb11-a2fb-48df370ead2d/data/name}}].SEGMENT = 'Platinum' OR [{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/1fe7caea-ae87-eb11-a2fb-48df370ead2d/data/name}}].SEGMENT = 'Gold' THEN '16531157541'
                ELSE '15581040571'
        END as POSID
FROM
	(
	SELECT
		Customer_id as customer_id,
		Last_Transaction_Date AS Last_Purchase_Date
	FROM
		{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/5c23cd6d-8ea2-eb11-a2fb-48df370f0129/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/5c23cd6d-8ea2-eb11-a2fb-48df370f0129/data/name}}] cd
	WHERE
		Last_Transaction_Date BETWEEN DATEADD(mm, -3, GETDATE()) AND DATEADD(dd, -30, GETDATE())
	) ab
	JOIN (
		SELECT
			PersonContactId,
			BannerAccountUser_Id,
			Account_postalCode__c,
			BannerAccount_Id,
			Account_uid__c,
			Account_FirstName,
			Account_LastName,
			Account_PersonEmail,
			Email_optin,
			Email_optout,
			Account_global_opt_out__c,
			SFSC_airmiles_Trimmed,
			Account_SFSC_airmiles__c,
			HomeStore_Region
		FROM
			{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/f2acf0bb-d606-eb11-a2f2-48df370f0128/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/f2acf0bb-d606-eb11-a2f2-48df370f0128/data/name}}]
		WHERE
			Email_optin = 'True'
			AND Email_optout = 'False'
			AND Account_global_opt_out__c = 'False'
			AND LEN(Account_SFSC_airmiles__c) = 11
			AND Optin_Source IS NOT NULL
			AND (BannerAccount_promotions__c != 'False' OR BannerAccount_promotions__c IS NULL)
			AND (Global_Suppression_Flag = 'False' OR Global_Suppression_Flag = '' OR Global_Suppression_Flag IS NULL)
	) cma ON ab.customer_id = cma.SFSC_airmiles_Trimmed
	LEFT JOIN
	(
		SELECT
			CUSTOMER_CARD_ID,
			SEGMENT
		FROM
			{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/1fe7caea-ae87-eb11-a2fb-48df370ead2d/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/1fe7caea-ae87-eb11-a2fb-48df370ead2d/data/name}}]
	) ltv ON cma.SFSC_airmiles_Trimmed = [{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/1fe7caea-ae87-eb11-a2fb-48df370ead2d/data/name}}].CUSTOMER_CARD_ID
	JOIN ENT._Subscribers s ON s.SubscriberKey = cma.PersonContactId
WHERE
	cma.SFSC_airmiles_Trimmed IN
		(SELECT hs.CUSTOMER_CARD_ID
			FROM {{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/8277c6ad-4e3a-ed11-ba3c-d4f5ef3de461/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/8277c6ad-4e3a-ed11-ba3c-d4f5ef3de461/data/name}}] hs
			WHERE HomeS_Banner= 'SOBEYS')
	AND cma.PersonContactId NOT IN
	(SELECT psd.PersonContactId
                                 FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/2c537478-19d0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/2c537478-19d0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/name}}] psd
                                 WHERE POSID IN ('16531157541','15581040571'))
	AND cma.PersonContactId NOT IN
			(SELECT PersonContactId
				FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/66d4af49-1cd0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/66d4af49-1cd0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/name}}])
	AND cma.PersonContactId NOT IN
			(SELECT PersonContactId
				FROM {{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/527fd191-6ed2-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/527fd191-6ed2-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/name}}] ba
				WHERE (ba.last_transaction_date__c > DATEADD(DD, -30, GETDATE())
											OR ba.avg_basket_value_0_12__c >= 50))
	AND cma.HomeStore_Region NOT IN ('atlantic')

data.name: Update_Order_Flag_Banner_Inactive
data.queryText:
SELECT AirmilesNumber, PersonContactID, 
CASE WHEN Last_Purchase_Date > EmailSendDate THEN 'True'
WHEN Last_Purchase_Date < EmailSendDate THEN 'False'
ELSE NULL
END as
Order_Placed
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/547db5f6-e92e-eb11-a2f2-48df370f018c/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/547db5f6-e92e-eb11-a2f2-48df370f018c/data/name}}]
WHERE EmailSendDate IS NOT NULL

data.name: Banner_Inactive_Tracking_Wave_1_Log
data.queryText:
SELECT a.Account_FirstName, a.Account_LastName, a.[Email 1 Send], a.[Email 2 Send], a.[Exit From],a.[Exit Time],a.Contact_Entry_Journey,
a.Contact_Entry_DE,a.BannerAccountUser_Id,a.PersonContactId,a.[PUSH 1 Sent],a.[AirmilesNumber],a.POSID, a.Eligible_Email_Offer,a.Eligible_Email_Offer_Timestamp
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/7b412a1f-af17-ed11-ba3c-d4f5ef3de461/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/7b412a1f-af17-ed11-ba3c-d4f5ef3de461/data/name}}] a
WHERE  a.Contact_Entry_DE NOT IN(
    select b.Contact_Entry_DE
    from {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/b20b198e-af17-ed11-ba3c-d4f5ef3de461/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/b20b198e-af17-ed11-ba3c-d4f5ef3de461/data/name}}] a
    join {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/7b412a1f-af17-ed11-ba3c-d4f5ef3de461/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/7b412a1f-af17-ed11-ba3c-d4f5ef3de461/data/name}}] b
    on a.PersonContactId = b.PersonContactId
    AND a.POSID = b.POSID)
AND a.[Exit Time] IS NOT NULL

data.name: Order_Count_Check_Banner_Inactive
data.queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT pi.AirmilesNumber, ab.Last_Purchase_Date, pi.PersonContactId, hst.HomeS_Banner as Current_Home_Banner
FROM
(SELECT cmd.Customer_id as AirmilesNumber, MAX(cmd.Last_Purchase_Date) as Last_Purchase_Date
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/17bfc847-8ea2-eb11-a2fb-48df370f0129/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/17bfc847-8ea2-eb11-a2fb-48df370f0129/data/name}}] cmd
GROUP BY cmd.Customer_id) ab
JOIN {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/2c537478-19d0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/2c537478-19d0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/name}}] pi ON
ab.AirmilesNumber = SUBSTRING(pi.AirmilesNumber,1,10)
JOIN {{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/8277c6ad-4e3a-ed11-ba3c-d4f5ef3de461/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/8277c6ad-4e3a-ed11-ba3c-d4f5ef3de461/data/name}}] hst
ON ab.AirmilesNumber = hst.CUSTOMER_CARD_ID

data.name: Current_Journey_Audience
data.queryText:
SELECT  bi.PersonContactId, bi.BannerAccountUser_Id, 'Banner Inactive Wave 1' as Current_Journey
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/ca9e6427-1ad0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/ca9e6427-1ad0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/name}}] bi
WHERE bi.[Exit From] IS NULL
AND bi.Contact_Entry_Journey IS NOT NULL

UNION

SELECT  bi.PersonContactId, bi.BannerAccountUser_Id, 'Banner Inactive Wave 2' as Current_Journey
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/ca9e6427-1ad0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/ca9e6427-1ad0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/name}}] bi
WHERE bi.[Exit From] IS NULL
AND bi.Contact_Entry_Journey IS NOT NULL

UNION

SELECT  bi.PersonContactId,bi.BannerAccountUser_Id, 'Predictive Spend Decline Wave 1' as Current_Journey
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/a812e310-8c3e-eb11-a2f5-48df370ead2d/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/a812e310-8c3e-eb11-a2f5-48df370ead2d/data/name}}] bi
WHERE bi.[Exit From] IS NULL
AND bi.Contact_Entry_Journey IS NOT NULL
AND bi.PersonContactId not in ('003DR00000lXTH0YAO','003DR00000lXTHyYAO')

UNION

SELECT  bi.PersonContactId,bi.BannerAccountUser_Id, 'Category Decline' as Current_Journey
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/8da301de-a92f-eb11-a2f2-48df370f018c/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/8da301de-a92f-eb11-a2f2-48df370f018c/data/name}}] bi
WHERE bi.[Exit From] IS NULL
AND bi.Contact_Entry_Journey IS NOT NULL

UNION

SELECT  bi.PersonContactId,bi.BannerAccountUser_Id, 'Predictive Spend Decline Wave 2' as Current_Journey
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/375dbac1-05d0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/375dbac1-05d0-eb11-a302-48df370ead2d/data/name}}] bi
WHERE bi.[Exit From] IS NULL
AND bi.Contact_Entry_Journey IS NOT NULL

UNION


SELECT bi.PersonContactId,'' as BannerAccountUser_Id, 'Airmiles to Banner' as Current_Journey
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/3536e689-a2b2-eb11-a2fe-48df370f018d/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/3536e689-a2b2-eb11-a2fe-48df370f018d/data/name}}] bi
WHERE bi.[Exit From] IS NULL
AND bi.Contact_Entry_Journey IS NOT NULL

UNION

SELECT bi.PersonContactId,bi.BannerAccountUser_Id, 'Banner Opt in Onboarding' as Current_Journey
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/5d113e37-48b1-eb11-a2fe-48df370f018d/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/5d113e37-48b1-eb11-a2fe-48df370f018d/data/name}}] bi
WHERE bi.[Exit From] IS NULL
AND bi.Contact_Entry_Journey IS NOT NULL
